OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy to start with hill fog
OL,6,Fand outbreaks of light rain or drizzle
OL,7,Ffor most. Cloud will then clear from
OL,8,Fthe east from late morning, with long
OL,9,Fafternoon sunny spells. Cooler than
OL,10,Frecently, especially in the onshore
OL,11,Fbreeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA bright evening, with plenty
OL,14,Fof late sunny spells. Mostly clear
OL,15,Fovernight, with a chance of frost in
OL,16,Frural parts. Hill fog may form over
OL,17,Fhigh ground. Winds falling light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
